data.description: Very functionally designed home is West Boise. 2 bedrooms above with generous sized family room adjoining the kitchen and eating area. Below boasts additional bedroom + den/office + bonus area and second family room. Newer LVP flooring throughout the lower level.Interior walls freshly painted. Enjoy entertaining with the east facing rear yard featuring a fire pit under the attached pergola and well-maintained green space. RV parking on side of home.
